#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: plogins-bump.php
msgid "Plogins Bump - Checkout Order Bump for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Plogins Bump – Checkout Order Bump für WooCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: plogins-bump.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/plogins-bump/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/plogins-bump/"

#. Description of the plugin
#: plogins-bump.php
msgid ""
"Show a one-click order-bump offer on the checkout so shoppers can add a "
"complementary product before they pay."
msgstr ""
"Zeige im Checkout ein Order-Bump-Angebot mit einem Klick, damit Käufer vor "
"der Zahlung ein ergänzendes Produkt hinzufügen können."

#. Author of the plugin
#: plogins-bump.php
msgid "WPPoland.com"
msgstr "WPPoland.com"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: plogins-bump.php
msgid "https://wppoland.com"
msgstr "https://wppoland.com"

#: plogins-bump.php:48
msgid "Plogins Bump requires WooCommerce to be active."
msgstr "Plogins Bump erfordert, dass WooCommerce aktiv ist."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:33
msgid "Bump – Order Bump"
msgstr "Bump – Order-Bump"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:34
msgid "Bump"
msgstr "Bump"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:50
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Einstellungen"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:80
msgid ""
"Show a one-click order-bump offer above the payment methods on the checkout."
" Ticking it adds the product to the order and recalculates the total before "
"payment."
msgstr ""
"Zeige im Checkout über den Zahlungsmethoden ein Order-Bump-Angebot mit einem"
" Klick. Wird es aktiviert, wird das Produkt zur Bestellung hinzugefügt und "
"die Summe vor der Zahlung neu berechnet."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:86
msgid "Enable order bump"
msgstr "Order-Bump aktivieren"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:90
msgid "Show the order-bump offer on the checkout."
msgstr "Order-Bump-Angebot im Checkout anzeigen."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:95
msgid "Bump product"
msgstr "Bump-Produkt"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:98
msgid "— Select a product —"
msgstr "— Produkt auswählen —"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:103
msgid ""
"A simple, purchasable product offered as the bump. Pick something cheap and "
"complementary."
msgstr ""
"Ein einfaches, kaufbares Produkt, das als Bump angeboten wird. Wähle etwas "
"Günstiges und Ergänzendes."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:107
msgid "Heading"
msgstr "Überschrift"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:108 src/Service/BumpService.php:99
msgid "One-time offer"
msgstr "Einmaliges Angebot"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:111
msgid "Checkbox label"
msgstr "Beschriftung des Kontrollkästchens"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:112 src/Service/BumpService.php:101
msgid "Yes, add this to my order!"
msgstr "Ja, zu meiner Bestellung hinzufügen!"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:115
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beschreibung"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:119
msgid "Override price"
msgstr "Preis überschreiben"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:122
msgid ""
"Optional special price for the bump line only (e.g. 19.00). Leave empty to "
"use the product's normal price."
msgstr ""
"Optionaler Sonderpreis nur für die Bump-Position (z. B. 19,00). Leer lassen,"
" um den normalen Produktpreis zu verwenden."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:126
msgid "Accent colour"
msgstr "Akzentfarbe"
